{"tid":322850,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 叉燒炒蛋","createTime":"2017-07-15T07:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T06:16:14.000Z","uid":74981,"like":30,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0040817dfd5ae3bd62102817914cba6eb7f374f2","tid":322850,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s13.postimg.org/kmbcck9pj/20170715_135935.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs13.postimg.org%2Fkmbcck9pj%2F20170715_135935.jpg&h=ca62a4aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>影片如下:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/saCExoYhCeA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsaCExoYhCeA&d=eue%2FMUzPyBi8wleLr1e%2Fc26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ca80a4f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/saCExoYhCeA</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>材料:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 雞蛋4隻<br />\n<br />\n2. 叉燒薄片數塊<br />\n<br />\n3. 九王少許<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>做法慨述:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 打蛋, 落半茶匙鹽, 胡椒粉少許打勻<br />\n<br />\n2. 爆香叉燒同九王<br />\n<br />\n3. 洗獲, 開大火燒紅獲, 落油朗獲, 熄火, 等獲溫度降, D煙走淨少少, 落蛋<br />\n<br />\n4. 落埋爆香過既叉燒同九王, 用推既方式去炒蛋, 唔好翻佢, 如果唔係會爛哂<br />\n<br />\n5. 推到岩岩熟, 上碟, 咁個炒蛋就唔會出水又唔會老, 完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9311d664fb2de06870eda70a21b7740936ea77ac","tid":322850,"uid":84212,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:13:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61617a94aa7d19b5c83d822112cf86d247a98d20","tid":322850,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:18:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b60c31cd428e6daaf0f97539277fdea170ba6434","tid":322850,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:19:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7d3811354c68fc614a16ed3491d604e441acc6c","tid":322850,"uid":60047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:19:15.000Z","msg":"Overcook wo ching"},{"pid":"7ce1f440557b78a0d71449bcb4f04ad6d6605a31","tid":322850,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:33:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Overcook wo ching</blockquote><br />\n小菜黎講，突登炒熟d。。<br />\n<br />\n其實係岩岩熟，咁就唔會出水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8309be10ce4faf81ed2f5e1267f5f3ee5671dd20","tid":322850,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0daf2dd33977a4921ace826d0decd6451234854a","tid":322850,"uid":100822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:41:56.000Z","msg":"切一切d叉燒好似好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3281ecca5ffb71a720c0cf5ae7d3e4565101555","tid":322850,"uid":51108,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:43:35.000Z","msg":"正!"},{"pid":"b5038f3f6e78f2883a11d47dd6fc36c559c33ba6","tid":322850,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8960980565900b7a3928cbdfe5aad17241520089","tid":322850,"uid":74981,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>切一切d叉燒好似好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係。。大片左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004aa0ca1c162b3b2fa380a852caee72034d7d30","tid":322850,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正!</blockquote><br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c4dcea5e2cd65c2c067c6753ad4e045b00eff8","