Time":"2017-07-15T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b89a4e7244911e4639d09e68121c4f417926369d","tid":322850,"uid":74981,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:06:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>建議<br />\n一係大師級，一係豬餿級<br />\n而家中下級唔好睇，傻既都煮到</blockquote><br />\n條肥鳩除咗呢啲下欄嘢識撚煮其他咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收皮啦死肥閪係到搞事</blockquote><br />\n唔覺有幾下欄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太多油似炸多啲<br />\n落洋蔥爆香佢再炒叉燒會正啲<br />\n起身切粒再落蛋<br />\n落啲蔥包一包佢<br />\n小小流心咁就又靚又香口</blockquote><br />\n巴打個idea幾好，不過本癲狗除左齋炒蛋會堅持炒滑蛋流心之外，其餘小菜類既炒蛋都喜歡炒到岩岩熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打平時都有下廚既興趣?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f03b47f75ee72183f39164956fb15cec31f08af","tid":322850,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:07:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥絲走啦屌你老母</blockquote><br />\nching ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2170b8323c0418c068704356425d00cd154862ff","tid":322850,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:09:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>建議<br />\n一係大師級，一係豬餿級<br />\n而家中下級唔好睇，傻既都煮到</blockquote><br />\n條肥鳩除咗呢啲下欄嘢識撚煮其他咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收皮啦死肥閪係到搞事</blockquote><br />\n唔覺有幾下欄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太多油似炸多啲<br />\n落洋蔥爆香佢再炒叉燒會正啲<br />\n起身切粒再落蛋<br />\n落啲蔥包一包佢<br />\n小小流心咁就又靚又香口</blockquote><br />\n巴打個idea幾好，不過本癲狗除左齋炒蛋會堅持炒滑蛋流心之外，其餘小菜類既炒蛋都喜歡炒到岩岩熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打平時都有下廚既興趣?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得閒偷下師睇下啲大廚煮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企有個冇理由唔偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3beabc2483c1e918abb5f912dfd8c481318d6e2d","tid":322850,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>建議<br />\n一係大師級，一係豬餿級<br />\n而家中下級唔好睇，傻既都煮到</blockquote><br />\n條肥鳩除咗呢啲下欄嘢識撚煮其他咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收皮啦死肥閪係到搞事</blockquote><br />\n唔覺有幾下欄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太多油似炸多啲<br />\n落洋蔥爆香佢再炒叉燒會正啲<br />\n起身切粒再落蛋<br />\n落啲蔥包一包佢<br />\n小小流心咁就又靚又香口</blockquote><br />\n巴打個idea幾好，不過本癲狗除左齋炒蛋會堅持炒滑蛋流心之外，其餘小菜類既炒蛋都喜歡炒到岩岩熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打平時都有下廚既興趣?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得閒偷下師睇下啲大廚煮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企有個冇理由唔偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nVery good<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835334edbf9b8f365b0d5e686579844973260d22","tid":322850,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:16:04.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677f713659d743beabb756747c2ec642a1fbb84d","tid":322850,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:24:34.000Z","msg":"叉燒咁大舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" 